        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Oracle Cloud(甲骨文)开启root登录]]></title>
        <id>https://pilipili.eu.org/FIQb3CITM/</id>
        <link href="https://pilipili.eu.org/FIQb3CITM/">
        </link>
        <updated>2022-11-05T13:02:37.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用密钥登录系统以后<br>
执行如下命令</p>
<pre><code>sudo -i
</code></pre>
<p>切换为root用户<br>
接着输入</p>
<pre><code>echo root:19960106ltd|sudo chpasswd root
sudo sed -i 's/^#\?PermitRootLogin.*/PermitRootLogin yes/g' /etc/ssh/sshd_config;
sudo sed -i 's/^#\?PasswordAuthentication.*/PasswordAuthentication yes/g' /etc/ssh/sshd_config;
</code></pre>
<p>其中19960106ltd为root的密码<br>
重启sshd服务</p>
<pre><code>sudo service sshd restart
</code></pre>
]]></content>
    </entry>
